{"tid":2027941,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"尖沙咀間執笠CD鋪終於收檔喇","createTime":"2020-05-21T14:49:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T08:57:42.000Z","uid":68125,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"2b263ba38ee56fccb89e85db55cb279604d8b732","tid":2027941,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T14:49:48.000Z","msg":"以下內容轉自K&rsquo;s Aviation<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/KSAviation1/photos/a.730162497186654/1307501279452770/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FKSAviation1%2Fphotos%2Fa.730162497186654%2F1307501279452770%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=%2FbZU6AtRr1oB2SY8YhhoV%2BaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=7ec8f087\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/KSAviation1/photos/a.730162497186654/1307501279452770/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/05/21/224850_6517866fc9efbdf773c21fddaf1d3921.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F05%2F21%2F224850_6517866fc9efbdf773c21fddaf1d3921.jpeg&h=9d03656a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n社會雖然情況預期會變得更差，但剷屎官小編隨筆想寫點輕鬆的，始終小編也有點思鄉病。<br />\n<br />\n如果大家有常常去尖沙咀的話，必定識圖中的影音鋪。最令小編最印象深刻的，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">始終都是影音鋪日日夜夜播著鄭秀文的歌，而歌曲也會與時俱進，由超過十年前的《終身美麗》，直至近期改播《信者得愛》</span></span>，比鄭秀文的唱片公司更落力宣傳鄭秀文，名副其實鄭秀文專業戶。坊間更有一句名言，就是未聽過鄭秀文唱歌，就不算到過 #尖沙咀。<br />\n<br />\n可惜由於租約期滿，該鋪於18/5搬遷，新址為<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">尖沙咀海防道31號</span></span>。據調查所知，新鋪面積約890平方呎，上手租客為龍城大藥房，月租大約50餘萬元，而藥房已於上星期已遷出。鄭秀文專業戶以約20萬元承租，每呎租225元。 武漢肺炎 對社會影響程度，連聽音樂的位置都會被影響。想不到，執笠已執超過十年，該鋪位真的有正式關門的一日。<br />\n<br />\n看來， 九龍公園的伯伯將來可以聽鄭秀文日唱夜唱。<br />\n<br />\nIG : <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CAcJiZnApos/?igshid=tt1qdz80rbqd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCAcJiZnApos%2F%3Figshid%3Dtt1qdz80rbqd&d=%2FbZU6AtRr1oB2SY8YhhoV%2BaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=a0774f67\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCAcJiZnApos%2F%3Figshid%3Dtt1qdz80rbqd&h=01d991fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CAcJiZnApos/?igshid=tt1qdz80rbqd</a>"},{"pid":"205dea59f0316ee15c652087d386e4904dd17067","tid":2027941,"uid":172190,"like":35,"dislike":4,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T14:59:17.000Z","msg":"一早應該執啦，嘈鳩住晒又冇人買"},{"pid":"ed52f4cb4c74db3c0bb76054444efafdaca8a6f9","tid":2027941,"uid":191966,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T15:16:51.000Z","msg":"佢d碟差不多貴信和一倍 其實唔明點捱到咁耐"},{"pid":"941fdbf6f793cd07d1a40b9ae8bfa119c6478651","tid":2027941,"uid":7331,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T15:24:25.000Z","msg":"搬去附近咋 唔記得邊到"},{"pid":"74d63ca843d3555ef426c4a361690b4209f89b69","tid":2027941,"uid":7331,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"941fdbf6f793cd07d1a40b9ae8bfa119c6478651","tid":2027941,"uid":7331,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T15:24:25.000Z","msg":"搬去附近咋 唔記得邊到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T15:25:15.000Z","msg":"冇睇內文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c7c7b60d94637645f4b96a0c58eee9283adb36d","tid":2027941,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T15:59:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2b3ef219194071ce628091b70e5f0f706a9a1769","tid":2027941,"uid":242444,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T16:30:03.000Z","msg":"別說新聞這麽假!!!!!!!!<br />\n天色這麽差!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"42e54d590f9f36c399dbf5a29aa95c1db3a61284","tid":2027941,"uid":82938,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b3ef219194071ce628091b70e5f0f706a9a1769","tid":2027941,"uid":242444,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T16:30:03.000Z","msg":"別說新聞這麽假!!!!!!!!<br />\n天色這麽差!!!!!!!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T16:32:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/face